 citizens’ successes.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aBanks and bankingzIsrael. 0aJewszPolandvBiography. 0aJews, PolishzIsraelvBiography. 7aBIOGRAPHY & AUTOBIOGRAPHY / Business.2bisacsh  aHolocaust.  aIsrael.  aMarcel Goldman.  aPolish-Jewish relations.  aeconomic history.  aeconomy of Israel.  ahistory of Israel.  ahistory of Jews.1 aB. Skotnicki, Aleksander, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRogalska-Chodecka, Katarzyna, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSkotnicki, Aleksander B., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAcademic Studies Press Complete eBook-Package 2022z978311076741408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2z978311076700108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Business and Economics 2022 Englishz978311099282308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishz978311099389908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Economics 2022z9783110992922oZDB-23-DBV40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781644698730?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781644698730423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781644698730/original  a978-3-11-076700-1  DG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2b2022  a978-3-11-076741-4  Academic Studies Press Complete eBook-Package 2022b2022  a978-3-11-099282-3  EBOOK PACKAGE Business and Economics 2022 Englishb2022  a978-3-11-099389-9  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishb2022  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LAEC  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_ESTMALL